ActOther Than Statutory Authority
SubjectCanada-French Republic Concerning the Provision of Mutual Logistic Support between the Canadian Armed Forces and the French Armed Forces ** Agreement **
PrecisOrder authorizing the Minister of Foreign Affairs to take the actions necessary to bring into force for Canada the AGREEMENT between the Government of Canada and the GOVERNMENT OF THE FRENCH REPUBLIC CONCERNING THE PROVISIONS OF MUTUAL LOGISTIC SUPPORT BETWEEN THE CANADIAN ARMED FORCES AND THE FRENCH ARMED FORCES.
